# Dashboard User Guide

The dashboard consists of two interactive pages.

## Page 1

Portfolio Overview

Displays:

- Total Loan Amount
- Number of Clients
- Outstanding Principal Balance
- Default Rate

Users can filter by:

- Loan Grade
- Loan Term

---

## Page 2

Risk Analysis

Displays:

- Default Rate by Loan Grade
- Default Rate by Interest Rate
- Default Rate by Income Category
- Default Rate by Debt-to-Income Ratio
- Default Rate by Employment Length

Navigation buttons allow movement between pages.
